[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說佛母出生三法藏般若",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0627c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "波羅蜜多經卷第十二",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0627c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝奉大夫試光祿卿",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0627c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傳法大師賜紫臣施護奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0627c15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惡者障法品第十一之二",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0627c16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者須菩提白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0627c17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何故惡魔於其長時勤作方便起諸障難，而令諸修菩薩法者，不得般若波羅蜜多正法聽受修習書持讀誦？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0627c17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告尊者須菩提言：「汝今當知，此般若波羅蜜多出生諸佛一切智，從一切智而復出生諸佛正法，從諸佛法出生無量無數眾生。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0627c21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛以其方便智力，普令眾生斷諸煩惱。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0627c23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "煩惱斷故，彼諸惡魔伺不得便，由不得便作障難故，心生苦惱。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0627c24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以苦惱心，是故長時勤作方便為諸難事，而令諸修菩薩法者，不得般若波羅蜜多正法聽受修習書持讀誦。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0627c26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸惡魔或作方便，於其初住大乘善男子前，作如是言：『汝所聽受非真般若波羅蜜多，我有經法，是真般若波羅蜜多，汝當隨我如是修學。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸惡魔以是方便欲壞善法，而初住大乘善男子等，少智少信，未得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提記，其心怯弱為魔所攝。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "魔所攝故，即不得此般若波羅蜜多正法，聽受修習書持讀誦。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此因緣者，應當覺知是為魔事。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸惡魔，或時現身作苾芻相，以壞法心，妄修菩薩甚深勝行，而返於中以聲聞果謂證實際。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此因緣者，應當覺知是為魔事。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸惡魔，以如是等種種方便，於此般若波羅蜜多正法作諸障難，不令有人書持讀誦。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故修菩薩法者，常當覺知，覺已遠離，即起勇猛勝精進心，堅固安住正念正知。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者須菩提白佛言：「如是，世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，善逝！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大珍寶聚，多有怨賊常欲伺求而為竊盜。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "珍寶難得，價直無量。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是因緣，多諸怨賊。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今此般若波羅蜜多大法寶聚，亦復如是多諸障難，常有惡魔伺求其便。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故所有初住大乘善男子等，少智少信其心怯弱，於此甚深廣大法中，不得聽受修習書持讀誦者，知彼皆是魔力所加。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a26_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復有人於如是等諸難事中，勇猛精進心不懈退，於此法門堅固修習書持讀誦者，豈非諸佛神通威力所加持耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628a26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如汝所說。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有人能於如是等諸難事中，得此法門聽受修習書持讀誦者，當知皆是諸佛如來神通威力共所護念。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼惡魔眾雖復長時勤作方便，於此法門起諸難事。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來、應供、正等正覺亦復長時勤作方便，於此般若波羅蜜多法門，以威神力加持護念。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "顯示世間品第十二之一",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告須菩提：「如世母人生育諸子，若一若十若百若千。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "忽於一時其母有疾，諸子各各勤求方便，多所療治。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "咸作是念：『云何令母速得遠離風癀痰[病-丙+(企-止+(套-大))]種種病苦，眼、耳、鼻、舌、身、意諸根輕安調適？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何令母飲食增進色力堅固，離諸苦受得大快樂？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何令母壽命長遠久住世間？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今我此身處於世間，從母所生生育甚難，以是因緣母恩為重。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有十方現在如來、應供、正等正覺亦復如是，各各以其神通威力加持護念，此般若波羅蜜多甚深法門，悲愍世間一切眾生，普令得聞書持讀誦。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸如來咸作是念：『云何得此般若波羅蜜多正法久住世間？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何得此般若波羅蜜多正法離破壞相？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何得此般若波羅蜜多正法，普令世間書持讀誦宣通流布，使諸惡魔不得其便？』",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來、應供、正等正覺於一切時勤作方便，稱讚護念般若波羅蜜多法門。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b24_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此般若波羅蜜多是諸佛母。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸如來、應供、正等正覺所有一切智，從般若波羅蜜多真實出生，而此般若波羅蜜多，能示諸佛及能顯示諸世間相。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628b27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有過去未來如來、應供、正等正覺，若已得、若當得，皆因是般若波羅蜜多故，成就阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及今現在十方無量阿僧祇世界一切如來、應供、正等正覺，住世說法廣為眾生作利益者，亦因是般若波羅蜜多故，成就阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知三世諸佛皆從般若波羅蜜多中來，般若波羅蜜多能善出生，是故般若波羅蜜多能示諸佛及能顯示諸世間相。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者須菩提白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如佛所說，般若波羅蜜多而能顯示世間相者，如來、應供、正等正覺當云何說為世間相？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願佛世尊廣為開示。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告尊者須菩提言：「佛說五蘊為世間相，所謂色、受、想、行、識，般若波羅蜜多顯示如是相。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提復白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何般若波羅蜜多示五蘊法為世間耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告須菩提：「當知般若波羅蜜多顯示五蘊壞無壞相，五蘊自性無作無生壞無所壞。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼空自性無作無生壞無所壞，無相、無願自性無作無生壞無所壞，法界自性亦無作無生壞無所壞，而此五蘊亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來、應供、正等正覺，說般若波羅蜜多示世間相。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來從般若波羅蜜多中來，能隨無量無數眾生性悉如實知。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來如實知耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂眾生自性即如實性，從般若波羅蜜多出生，如來亦復從般若波羅蜜多出生，是故如來能隨無量無數眾生性皆如實知。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由實了知眾生性故，乃至無量無數眾生一切心行亦如實知。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0628c29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以了知無量無數眾生心行故，是故佛說般若波羅蜜多示世間相。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生攝心亂心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生攝心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂若集若散住法性中如實了知。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如實知，是即了知眾生攝心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是攝心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生亂心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂住法性中知心無相，心無相故，即無盡無不盡。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如實了知盡無盡相，是即了知眾生亂心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是亂心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生無盡心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生無盡心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂知心無壞，心無壞故即心無生滅，無生滅故即無住無依，無有盡相猶如虛空廣大無盡，而心相亦然。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是無盡心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生染心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生染心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知染心如實相即非染心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是染心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生離染心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生離染心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知染心自性，即離染心中無離染心相。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是離染心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629a28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生諸能緣心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生能緣心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知阿賴耶等諸能緣心無能緣心相。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是能緣心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生諸能取心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生能取心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知無所取相，取相離故即不可取。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是能取心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生諸有漏心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生有漏心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心無自性，無自性故即無分別。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是有漏心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生諸無漏心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生無漏心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心無自性即非心分。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是無漏心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生貪心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生貪心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知若住貪即心不如實，若心如實即不住貪，於平等法中無貪心可得。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是貪心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生離貪心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生離貪心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629b29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心如實相，若貪、若離貪俱不可得，由不可得故即無離貪心相。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是離貪心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生恚心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生恚心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心住空寂，離所緣相無諸分別。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是恚心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生離恚心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生離恚心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心法無二從真實生。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是離恚心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c13_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生癡心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生癡心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知若心住於癡即心不如實，若心如實即不住於癡。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是癡心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c18_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生離癡心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生離癡心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知若心有所著即心隨癡相，若心住如實即不隨癡相，由如是故無離癡心相可得。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是離癡心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生過失心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生過失心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知若心生過失即心不如實，若心如實即不生過失，於平等法中無過失心可得。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0629c29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是過失心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a02_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生離過失心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生離過失心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知若心有所著即過失隨生。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若心住如實即不生過失，由如是故無離過失心相可得。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a07_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是離過失心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生廣心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生廣心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知是心不增不減無住無著。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是廣心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生非廣心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生非廣心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心無處所，無處所故即無起作亦無增廣。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是非廣心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生大心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生大心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知是心平等自性無差別。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是大心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生非大心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生非大心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心無來去。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是非大心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630a29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生無量心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生無量心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心無依止，無依止故即無限量。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是無量心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生現心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生現心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知諸心自性無所顯現。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是現心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生非現心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生非現心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心無形相自性離故，由性離故非現非不現。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是非現心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生勝上心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生勝上心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知若心住如實即無所生亦無所有，是為勝上。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能知無量無數眾生如是勝上心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b23_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生無上心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生無上心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心無所得離諸戲論。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是無上心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630b28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生定心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生定心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知是心平等，平等法中無定亂相，猶如虛空寂無所動。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是定心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生非定心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生非定心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心無等等即心平等，心平等故而不可得非定心相。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是非定心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生解脫心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生解脫心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知眾生自性解脫，彼眾生性即解脫性。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能知無量無數眾生如是解脫心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生非解脫心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生非解脫心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知心性無來無去無住，非過去未來現在三世可得，解脫性離，即不可得非解脫相。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是非解脫心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來因般若波羅蜜多故，如實了知無量無數眾生不可見心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何如來知眾生不可見心耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂了知彼眾生心，無所生無所成，無分別無所取，離諸相不可見，慧眼、天眼尚不能觀，豈況肉眼。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來因般若波羅蜜多故，能知無量無數眾生如是不可見心。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0630c29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告須菩提：「如是等諸心，如來因般若波羅蜜多故，一一如實了知。",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0631a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是義故，般若波羅蜜多而能顯示諸世間相。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0631a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說佛母出生三法藏般若波羅蜜多經卷第十二",
        "from": "T08n0228_012:0631a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]